&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’re VaynerMedia! &lt;/strong&gt;VaynerMedia is a global integrated creative and media agency, built for today&#39;s consumers. As the Modern Agency of Record, it understands the nuances of today&#39;s attention landscape, empowering brands to win attention, drive relevance, and deliver business results. Founded in 2009, by Gary Vaynerchuk, the independently owned agency operates in 15 offices worldwide, including Amsterdam, Bangkok, Chicago, New Delhi, Kuala Lumpur, London, Los Angeles, Mexico City, Miami, New York, Tokyo, Toronto, Singapore, and Sydney. VaynerMedia is part of the VaynerX family of companies&lt;strong&gt;. &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Culture is our key and Empathy is how we build it. VaynerMedia EMEA is strong with a world-class combination of diverse backgrounds collaborating to put forward innovative, creative and strategic solutions to the one advantage that stands the test of time – PEOPLE. Day in and day out, we propel some of the biggest brands in the world to the intersection of attention and culture.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The PITCH.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking to make the move and step up into a leadership role? Then this could be for you. We&#39;re looking for another ACD to join the creative leadership team. You&#39;ll be the go-to creative for a couple of our accounts, leading creative teams with a focus on the best work possible. Guiding and shaping great ideas that hit the client briefs and make us all proud. Adept at presenting, you are able to work alongside client partnership teams to build and grow clients. You&#39;re used to negotiating your way to the best creative answers for the campaigns whilst keeping clients on side. But that doesn&#39;t mean you won&#39;t challenge and know how to defend the work with grace and meaning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here’s where you come in…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver creative solutions for a variety of clients and industries. Executes work on your own as well as managing teams and approving work of your assigned creative team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support CD/ECD to mentor and manage creatives and teams. Acts as a quality control and brand steward to lead creators, senior creators, creators across different disciplines such as content creation, design, copy and edit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-departmentally to develop a high variety of ideas that meets creative and strategic criteria (client briefs, feedback, client KPIs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideate and conceptualize high-engaging thinking that reflects brand&#39;s aesthetic and style guidelines; maintaining aesthetic, tone, and brand consistency across all deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fosters positive relationships among the internal teams, the creative department, direct reports, other agency partners, and clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide and lead the team to generate a wide range of concepts, high-level copywriting and content strategy, providing evaluation, mentorship, counsel, and determining assignments, promotions, and incentives as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing and developing junior members to become confident with leadership and presentation skills, always monitoring performance and progress, and managing up to the leadership team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands, articulates, and strategically applies the latest platform/industry/creative trends and digital best practices, knowing social inside out and always seeking the next opportunity in this space for your brands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Masters the industry best practices and the social platforms we love, as well as being willing to learn and articulate the unique VaynerMedia POV on each.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attends client meetings to communicate creative vision and processes, bringing stellar presentation skills to the table with the ability to read a room and adjust style

