&lt;li&gt;Strategic understanding of traditional, digital, and social-specific media planning &amp;amp; buying, along with the proper metrics of success and measurement opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear attention-to-detail and organizational excellence to ensure flawless delivery of planned strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
