&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT VAYNERMEDIA&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VaynerMedia is a global integrated creative and media agency, built for today&#39;s consumers. As the Modern Agency of Record, it understands the nuances of today&#39;s attention landscape, empowering brands to win attention, drive relevance, and deliver business results. Founded in 2009, by Gary Vaynerchuk, the independently owned agency operates in 15 offices worldwide, including Amsterdam, Bangkok, Chicago, New Delhi, Kuala Lumpur, London, Los Angeles, Mexico City, Miami, New York, Tokyo, Toronto, Singapore, and Sydney. VaynerMedia is part of the VaynerX family of companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Producer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: New York, NY&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is full-time, and requires a hybrid work schedule (in-office and on-location). VaynerMedia NY headquarters is located in Hudson Yards, NYC.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp; VaynerMedia is a global integrated creative, media, and production focused agency, headquartered in New York City. The agency is known for putting &lt;em&gt;social at the center&lt;/em&gt; of brand strategy and content creation, blending traditional Madison Avenue thinking with modern, digital-first storytelling to drive relevance and business results for clients across industries. Our agency’s philosophy emphasizes understanding audiences deeply and creating platform-native content that turns attention into action, backed by its integrated model and strong partnerships with major media platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are: &lt;/strong&gt;You are a creative producer with multidisciplinary production execution skills. Your craft spans agency production, line production, post production and event-based activations with a strong production company mindset. You are both creatively curious and operationally minded. You are a hands-on producer who completely immerses oneself in the work by leaning in to shepherd complex campaigns across multiple channels, for content that requires real-time culture and relevance opportunities. You are adaptable to evolving ideas and new ways of thinking. You think of the big picture but do not forget the details. You are comfortable navigating agency and client dynamics, and your strength lies in translating creative ambition into clear, executable production plans. Working under the guidance of Senior and Executive Producers, you take ownership of the day-to-day production execution that brings campaigns to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring a production lens to early ideation to unlock bold, scalable ideas and to navigate trade-offs between speed, cost, craft, partners, formats and output.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with internal agency partners as the production voice to assess project feasibility and approach, identifying risks, efficiencies, and executional opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end production for 360 campaigns by building budgets with talent locations, schedule, and post considerations in mind, with budgets ranging from $100k-$500k+&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lead in hands-on production bidding, and step in as a line producer, when required

